<%
// This is a shortcut for using IFSummaryStart, then summary text, then
// IFSummaryEnd. It's used to create the summary box at the top of a page.
//
// Parameters:
//
//  $0 - Path of IDL file
//  $1 - The interface's parent class
//  $2 - "scriptable" or "not scriptable"
//  $3 - The last Gecko version the interface changed in
//  $4 - A summary of the interface (optional)
//  $5 - The Gecko version the interface was introduced in (optional)
//  $6 - The Gecko version the interface was deprecated in (optional)
//  $7 - The Gecko version the interface was removed in (optional)
//
%>

<%-await template("IFSummaryStart", [$0, $2])%>
<%
var summary = $4;
if (!$4) {
  summary = "<i>Please add a summary to this article.</i>";
}
%>
<%-summary%>
<%-await template("IFSummaryEnd", [$1, $3, $5, $6, $7])%>
